{"tid":1144192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南生圍「婚紗橋守護者」吊頸亡","createTime":"2019-05-08T03:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T10:17:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"41ab14ddd20926876607230af8e5659ac8c24d37","tid":1144192,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190508/20673409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190508%2F20673409&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2Fciukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=9a148d7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190508%2F20673409&h=12942f4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190508/20673409</a><br />\n<br />\n南生圍「婚紗橋守護者」吊頸亡<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190508/large/08la5p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190508%2Flarge%2F08la5p6.jpg&h=007cefd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n方兆基前年和根叔慶祝新建婚紗橋及立下牌匾。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】自稱「南生圍佬」曾幫手修建南生圍婚紗橋的55歲方兆基（Ringo），疑因不堪癌病纏身，10日前發「永別」短訊給家人後不知所終，至昨日被人發現他在元朗山貝洪田村一個山墳後面樹叢吊頸身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警指因病厭世<br />\n<br />\n55歲的方兆基報住大生圍一間村屋，據知，他早前發現患有末期肺癌，致情緒低落，上月27日缺席報名參加的天后寶誕會景巡遊表演舞獅，當晚在天水圍嘉湖銀座露面後便告失蹤。其間，家人接獲他短訊，寫有「永別」兩字，家人兩日後報警。警方接報曾發相呼籲市民找尋。<br />\n<br />\n昨日中午12時許，有鋸樹工人在元朗山貝洪田村鋸樹期間，在一個山墳後面數米兩棵樹之間，發現一名男子頸纏繩索掛在樹上，立即報警。警員及消防員到場將男子解下，證實他已死去多時，屍身已腐爛。警員在死者身上撿獲銀包及證件，證實死者為失蹤的方兆基，警員未有撿獲遺書，調查後相信他因病厭世。<br />\n<br />\n方去年曾接受《蘋果》記者採訪，稱在南生圍住過十多年，自稱「南生圍佬」，直到1974年，方兆基小學畢業，因地產商買下南生圍土地，才搬離南生圍。兩年前颱風「天鴿」襲港將南生圍第四代婚紗橋摧毀，方協助在橫水渡撐船建造婚紗橋的根叔，用環保木重新鋪橋，被網民喻為「婚紗橋守護者」。前年12月尾，他在第五代新橋旁立下紅底金字的「婚紗橋」牌匾惹來批評，其後方兆基將牌匾重新設計，並在去年底更換成木製牌匾。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁瑞帆  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n尊位欠薪40萬 六人入稟追討"},{"pid":"7e9c0603cdca2f8787fa1430ee7be0a3d536dad6","tid":1144192,"uid":23758,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"家人兩日後報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7414441f97d891511a7334b10b3cd2eaa97ca1a","tid":1144192,"uid":71508,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:01:47.000Z","msg":"有陰謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f2f5018425e4bf487776eb278beef779cfc8d5","tid":1144192,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"7e9c0603cdca2f8787fa1430ee7be0a3d536dad6","tid":1144192,"uid":23758,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"家人兩日後報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:11:07.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57973acba582239bd87745984b3e1498f3bdec7","tid":1144192,"uid":2429,"like":34,"dislike":4,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"d9f2f5018425e4bf487776eb278beef779cfc8d5","tid":1144192,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"7e9c0603cdca2f8787fa1430ee7be0a3d536dad6","tid":1144192,"uid":23758,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"家人兩日後報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:11:07.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:12:27.000Z","msg":"未夠48小時唔受理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d0583c338e7f65ad4a688488fcf8c7f9e73782","tid":1144192,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3be76978d52172dd85e3b2f5239a6bd3746c23","tid":1144192,"uid":143033,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:29:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69097de70c0a110caeb01a4726a83e36ffa1882a","tid":1144192,"uid":16567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"個牌好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc3836334e1141a0d39700839e9c1fc5907d3b8","tid":1144192,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f3be76978d52172dd85e3b2f5239a6bd3746c23","tid":1144192,"uid":143033,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:29:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"燒比佢"},{"pid":"576d771d626212cf3b50d1ddff705468cd3b9b58","tid":1144192,"uid":55851,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:18:22.000Z","msg":"南生圍背後利益千絲萬縷，上次放完火已經係警告"},{"pid":"d5302663d23360dac898b1db28a3b7a442a44860","tid":1144192,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:20:59.000Z","msg":"另一份報章話佢無食煙"},{"pid":"f7d3e1224c30ea389be3fe6b3cf239dbf70a0b31","tid":1144192,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d4095aae8e577ed25f503305274a2bd61405a8","tid":1144192,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b57973acba582239bd87745984b3e1498f3bdec7","tid":1144192,"uid":2429,"like":34,"dislike":4,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"d9f2f5018425e4bf487776eb278beef779cfc8d5","tid":1144192,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"7e9c0603cdca2f8787fa1430ee7be0a3d536dad6","tid":1144192,"uid":23758,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"家人兩日後報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:11:07.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:12:27.000Z","msg":"未夠48小時唔受理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T06:52:12.000Z","msg":"不少市民誤以為失蹤人士要失蹤超過24 / 48小時才可以報案，本集旨在教育市民正確的知識，並提醒市民帶備足夠的資料報案，例如身份證號碼、近照、病歷等等，以增加報案效率。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hdY1o0RXylc?t=319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhdY1o0RXylc%3Ft%3D319&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2Fciukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=592f6f00\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hdY1o0RXylc?t=319</a><br />\n當遇到親人失蹤時，市民雖然急於尋找家人，但往往卻誤以為家人要失蹤超過48小時才能報案。事實上，警方在處理失蹤人士案件方面，並無任何失蹤時間的限制。只要大家發現有親人失蹤，遍尋不獲，又擔心失蹤者的安危時，已可報警求助。<br />\n另一方面，市民在報稱家人失蹤時，往往會因為急於報案，而忘記帶備足夠資料。最常見的例子，便是忘記帶失蹤者的身份證明文件，又或是未能提供失蹤者的近照。為更有效地尋找失蹤人士，報案人應提供失蹤者的詳細資料，例如身份證明文件、病歷、失蹤時衣著及近照等等。而所提供的近照，最好貼近失蹤者失蹤前的外貌，同時報案人亦應向警方描述失蹤者的特徵，例如身上會否有任何疤痕，或失蹤者是否行動不便。以上的細節均能協助警方的搜索行動，以便盡快尋回失蹤者。"},{"pid":"55b7ea3ef92aa96510ca3c9d511bf50d83b5a8a4","tid":1144192,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90d4095aae8e577ed25f503305274a2bd61405a8","tid":1144192,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b57973acba582239bd87745984b3e1498f3bdec7","tid":1144192,"uid":2429,"like":34,"dislike":4,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"d9f2f5018425e4bf487776eb278beef779cfc8d5","tid":1144192,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:11:07.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" 